  "title": "Technical Support Engineer (RF, P25, DMR, radio))",
  "description": "<p><strong>about company</strong></p>\n<p>I am currently working with a global leader in communications solutions; broadband, radio network etc.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>2-3 rounds of interview. Office located at Ubi. Flexible working arrangement.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>about job</strong></p>\n<p>● An intermediate practical knowledge of analogue, P25 and DMR radio systems, including RF system design, installation,</p>\n<p>and support.</p>\n<p>● A developed practical knowledge radio terminal features and programming.</p>\n<p>● Highly developed customer service and diplomacy skills.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>skills and requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>● Min 3 years’ experience in an ICT or wireless communications technical role</p>\n<p>● Engineering degree in a related field or equivalent work experience</p>\n<p>● Experience with Land Mobile Radio equipment, P25, DMR, conventional, trunking, simulcast systems and LTE technologies would be beneficial.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>To apply online please use the 'apply' function, alternatively you may contact Stella at 96554170 (EA: 94C3609 /R1875382)</p>",
